:0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T16:02:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實可以睇住佢地慢慢老去都算一種福氣...</blockquote><br />\n我有時都係咁諗但係諗諗下又唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8c13d8983884d51843369ac97d2a2608ce7e0a","tid":232981,"uid":109012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T16:03:18.000Z","msg":"間唔中夜晚訓唔著都會諗諗下佢地老左好多, 冇左佢地點算  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n之後喊, 喊完訓醒又唔記得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4efe5fe8ae536f5058b8e8999eabea8cf0a3c344","tid":232981,"uid":85205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T16:04:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老豆就快60<br />\n最近啲一年成日咳同氣喘<br />\n又死都唔育去睇醫生<br />\n都唔知點好</blockquote><br />\n鼓勵佢睇中醫？年紀大嘅人對中醫唔係咁抗拒。而且叫調理身體，唔係有病先睇中醫"},{"pid":"1fdf7a843d22beda2c6cda01aa33e5e443869f7e","tid":232981,"uid":85205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T16:05:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇人老豆老母個樣好後生，自己個樣就好老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我會畀人以為係我呀媽個細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你同阿媽差幾多年啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67f4842385faa9506e43f575087921a75b857928","tid":232981,"uid":85205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T16:05:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>希望兩老身體健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大家咁話<img src=\"