\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想佢去睇下醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但又驚睇完醫生發現有d病，<br />\n我同佢都一定會唔開心，唔想面對</blockquote><br />\n呢d盡早啊。宜家仲有得救唔開心，好過第日無得救唔開心"},{"pid":"938818bd06e3ea3d52d60518c46f8b933a05e51a","tid":232981,"uid":85205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T16:53:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真係要好好孝順父母喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申媽媽上年驗到有末期cancer 今年初就走咗</blockquote><br />\n咁巴打係咪睇化咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁又唔係 我今年都係讀緊yr1咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過真係要好好珍惜愛錫你嘅親人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嘩，巴打都好犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8936606aed11de64d240480c10eb09429b70aacc","tid":232981,"uid":85205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T16:56:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有呀嫲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢都成80幾<br />\n細個我一放假就探佢<br />\n依家忙到過年都冇去揾佢<br />\n<br />\n有次為左探佢棄左半份assignment睇下佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近排見佢成日病<br />\n好擔心</blockquote><br />\n對阿婆阿嫲咁孝順好少有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打加油"},{"pid":"15e299df5711a52dbc81fa7926aab7b4df60f043","tid":232981,"uid":85205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T16:57:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢排成日都咁諗 好怕有日媽媽唔係度 我會喊到屋企水浸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我會喊但係阿媽成日係屋企，唔可以喊太大聲比佢知，好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"506e3e9c391921cc1b3a76ac1b7158f37eb3c7c8","tid":232981,"uid":85205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T17:02:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔止父母 我好驚所有親人好快老<br />\n細細個成日嫌佢哋管三管四好煩 而家知有人煩都係一件好事 係得佢哋先會一直原諒同包容自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但人總會老 唯有盡自己努力去孝順佢哋 陪多啲佢哋 彌補返細個唔識諗成日想逃離佢哋同hurt佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無錯，以前我成日出去玩玩到好夜先返屋企。每次返屋企阿媽都係廳唔訓等我，之後鬧我出街。我次次都好炆。有次佢勁大聲話「你知唔知阿媽我擔心你咋」。聽到之後我即刻收聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c674ab9bcbe6ea5dfc2dc542401898ac4ac20c","tid":232981,"uid":85205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T17:02:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家每年都帶媽咪去一次旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家唔好成日掛住同朋友玩<br />\n襯父母仲行得走得 帶佢地睇下呢個世界<br />\n影多啲相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nps.爸爸唔肯申請護照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想，到我有能力唔知佢仲行唔行得郁呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecae31294dd9b691d3d60d021a9b939eb40bdd9b","tid":232981,"uid":108324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T17:10:42.000Z","msg":"呀媽差唔多成三字尾生我 宜加都就黎六十<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老豆仲老多幾年 成日都諗點解我唔可以早十幾年出世 咁就可以同佢地相處得耐啲 有時候見到啲fd既父母個樣仲咁young好羨慕 感覺佢地仲有大把時間可以係有父母既看顧下成長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打打下都想喊"},{"pid":"89d1ea5678e87291647b2fab8b2e35e3176b3a99","tid":232981,"uid":92606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T17:11:30.000Z","msg":"以前覺得爸媽去